Package com.retriage.retriage.services

Interface PatientPoolTmpService

All Known Implementing Classes:
PatientPoolTmpServiceImp
public interface PatientPoolTmpService
Service interface defining the contract for managing PatientPoolTmp entities. Implementations of this interface handle the business logic related to patient pool templates, used for configuring pools when creating new events.
